I am fatigued but if I give into the fatigue I know it only leads to awakened and energetic misery. Be peaceful with the body, such entertainments aren’t peaceful, they’re a strain, a sour and twisted one. They will only work to sour and corrupt you, so that you can’t be peaceful with the intellect. If you are fatigued, then be slow for a time, that’s it. 



